data.description:
**Contractors Showdown** delivers an immersive military-styled VR First-Person Shooter experience. Engage in heart-pounding combat with **60 players**, navigate a vast and detailed **16km²(6.17763mi²)** map. The game centers around a thrilling Battle Royale game mode, where strategic prowess and combat skills are paramount.  Gear up for intense battles, dynamic team play, and a visually stunning VR environment that thrusts players into the forefront of military actions.
{978837273958553}

# Realistic Combat Experience
Grip your guns, reload your mags, and pull your triggers in this immersive ground-zero military combat experience. Navigate the battlefield, aim with true precision, and execute real-time warfare strategies to outlast every opponent!
{956368703161290}

# Adapt and Conquer
Tailor your arsenal to your play style in your own headquarters with our highly customizable loadout system. Coordinate seamlessly with your team using spatial voice chat for a strategic advantage.
{448213471030033}

# An Expanse to Discover, Master, and Conquer
Get ready for an epic showdown on a 16km² battlefield where you can assemble your ideal squad of one, two, or three Contractors! Utilize the surrounding terrain, such as buildings, landmarks, hills, and other structures, to gain a tactical advantage over other skilled contractors and emerge victorious in a **60-player** royale!
{1600961607355051}
